issue.title: ReminderClient.updateReminder()
issue.body: Needed for editing a reminder - probably requires that Reminder.id is a constant, randomly-generated string rather than its fields' hash

issue.title: Get push notification token
issue.body: Need to get a push notification token on the client and send it to the server - this will allow the server to send push notifs. See https://thatthinginswift.com/remote-notifications/
